<doc id="287586" wikidata="Q61659029" url="?curid=287586" title="James Bunning">
<text>James Bunning may refer to:

* Jim Bunning (1931–2017), American baseball pitcher and politician 
* James Bunstone Bunning (1802–1863), British architect</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q918265" start="31" end="42" title="Jim Bunning" label="Jim Bunning"/>
