<doc id="287671" wikidata="Q1122005" url="?curid=287671" title="Juon">
<text>Juon may refer to:

* Paul Juon, noted classical composer
* &quot;Ju-On&quot;, a series of horror films originating in Japan; remade in English as &quot;The Grudge&quot; by the same director</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q171509" start="22" end="31" title="Paul Juon" label="Paul Juon"/>
<link wikidata="Q1200011" start="66" end="71" title="Ju-On" label="Ju-On"/>
